Extract the configuration command from the user's message.

Supported command types:
- set_project_name — the user names or renames the group/chat (payload: {"name": "project name"})
  Examples: "this is the Alpha project group", "name this group Beta", "remember: this group is for project Gamma"

Return JSON without additional text in the format:
{"type": "command_type", "payload": {"key": "value"}}

If the command type cannot be determined — use type "unknown".
If any payload field is missing — leave it as an empty string.

Always respond in English.
